&lt;a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/424290515?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title" target="_blank"&gt;2020 诺贝尔奖为什么只颁给了发现丙肝病毒的科学家，却不给研制出治愈丙肝药物的人？&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;
            </description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Clover青子</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 06 Oct 2020 13:00:10 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://www.zhihu.com/question/424268740/answer/1509011958</guid></item></channel></rss>